{"id":23298,"type":4,"name":"Drawn: Dark Flight","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/58/5b/23298_35ARE.jpg","rating":{"total":53,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":0,"6":6,"7":20,"8":21,"9":4,"10":1},"score":7.4},"summary":"《谜画之塔2：暗夜飞行（Drawn：Dark Flight）》是《谜画之塔》系列的第二款作品，是一款点击式冒险游戏，由Big Fish工作室开发。\r\n在前作中，玩家扮演一个偶然闯入巨大高塔的无名角色，这里曾经是魔法要塞，玩家立即被卷入到了拯救一位年轻的魔法公主的任务之中，她的名字叫作Iris，拥有梦中预言的能力。\r\nIris被锁在了这座塔的塔顶，这是为了保护她，因为一个恶魔国王正在追杀她，妄图消灭皇室血裔的最后一名成员；Iris的整个皇室家族都拥有相同的能力，这也使他们的世界经历了短暂的黄金时代。\r\n然而恶魔国王从另一片大陆上前来，杀死了除Iris之外的所有人，征服并统治了谜画世界。\r\n在游戏中，玩家必须面对极具挑战性而又有趣的谜题，这些谜题散布在Iris的画作中和高塔之内，背后有着许多秘密。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>谜画之塔2：暗夜飞行</li><li><span>开发: </span><a href=\"/person/9950\">Big Fish Games</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>Drawn The Painted Tower Ⅱ:Dark Flight</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Drawn II：Dark Flight Collector's Edition</li><li><span>平台: </span>PC</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>iOS</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>PUZ</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>1</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2010年08月31日</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://www.drawngame.com/games/dark-flight</li><li><span>简写: </span>Drawn II</li>","collection":{"wish":7,"collect":65,"doing":1,"dropped":3},"tags":[{"name":"解谜","count":21},{"name":"PC","count":20},{"name":"AVG","count":13},{"name":"独立游戏","count":9},{"name":"BigFish","count":6},{"name":"DRAWN","count":5},{"name":"还不错","count":5},{"name":"PUZ","count":4},{"name":"精致","count":3},{"name":"解謎","count":2},{"name":"indie","count":2},{"name":"……","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":9950,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/95/0a/9950_prsn_4JJLz.jpg","name":"Big Fish Games","desc":"开发"}],"relations":[{"id":23297,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/5c/ba/23297_b5Eul.jpg","title":"Drawn: The Painted Tower","type":"前传","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/23297"},{"id":25317,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/14/1e/25317_zU8KN.jpg","title":"Drawn: Trail of Shadows","type":"续集","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/25317"}],"like":[{"id":25445,"name":"谜画之塔3阴影